{
  "stem": "20616.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, well, first junior high school, and then I went to DeWitt Clinton High school in the Bronx for a while and then we moved to Queens.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I graduated from Newtown High School in Queens.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, actually I went to City College at night.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no plans for anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I knew that I was going to be drafted into the army.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was just the beginning of when United States went into the-- went to war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I took non-matriculated courses in subjects that interested me-- international law, economics, and accounting, for practical purposes, not to get any degree.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my first job actually after graduating high school was splitting hair in a brush factory.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Sounds funny today.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Brushes were made from horse tails.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we got shipments in of chopped horse tails, more or less.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We had to take the hair and process it, bake it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And, and there's a hair splitting machine to split the ends of the hair to make it softer-- the ends softer for the brushes.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I lasted about two weeks at that job.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I understand that Henry Kissinger-- a lot of my so-called career was in parallel to Henry Kissinger's.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I also went to dancing school with him at one time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER] There was a refugee, a, a former gym teacher who became a dancing teacher.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we, as teenagers, were supposed to learn manners and dancing and also meet the proper girls that way.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And it was a social sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we went to dancing school for awhile.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In fact, I have an, a biography of Kissinger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that school is mentioned in the book, Kissinger.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he never became a star pupil of hers.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
